  "title": "Senior Java Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Requirement :<br />Strong experience in Java 8, Spring Boot, and Microservices development.<br />Expertise in RESTful API design, HTTP protocols, and distributed systems.<br />Proven experience designing event-driven architectures.<br />5+ years of hands-on experience with AWS Cloud services (EC2, S3, Lambda, RDS, CloudWatch, IAM).<br />Solid understanding of object-oriented design, SOLID principles, and SOA.<br />Experience working in Agile/Scrum environments.<br />Demonstrated leadership and mentoring experience.<br /></p><p>Responsibilities:<br />Design and develop scalable applications using Java 8, Spring Boot, and Microservices.<br />Build and maintain RESTful APIs using SOLID, SOA, and modern OOP principles.<br />Design and implement event-driven, microservices architectures.<br />Deliver and optimize AWS cloud solutions using EC2, S3, Lambda, RDS, CloudWatch, and IAM.<br />Mentor and guide a team of 8+ engineers, ensuring code quality and engineering standards.<br />Participate in Agile/Scrum ceremonies and collaborate with cross-functional teams.<br />Contribute to QBRs and strategic technical discussions with leadership.<br />Continuously learn and apply emerging technologies (AI, Python, AWS).</p>",
